    "126221446": {
      "title": "New transform iterative method for solving some Klein-Gordon equations",
      "abstract": "Abstract In this study, we treat some Klein-Gordon equations (KGEs). We propose a novel iterative approach called the Elzaki iterative method (EIM). This method, which clearly depends on the choice of the initial values, is based on the new iteration method (NIM) and the Elzaki transformation. We show that the EIM could be more valid and reliable approach than the NIM. We propose an analytical approximation of a solution for KGEs for which only a few iterations are necessary to obtain a semi-analytical solution without a loss of precision."
    }
